			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- goto 163.75, 23.23, 551.75&#xD;&#xA;- Kill Bex and Danis (Ctrl+Shift+K).&#xD;&#xA;- oe readyattackonden&#xD;&#xA;- oe attackondentieflingvictory&#xD;&#xA;- SetGlobalOsirisFlag DEN_AttackOnDen_Event_TieflingPartyInvitation&#xD;&#xA;- Go to camp. Skip through the dialogues.&#xD;&#xA;- In camp find Vatas. Talk to him." />
